CE

CE <- as.data.frame(subset(CE_excel, select = -c(ID, group, gender_group)))
CE <- CE[, which(colMeans(!is.na(CE)) > 0.7)]
CE <- as_tibble(CE)
# Replace with minimum value in range of DF
selected_columns <- c(1:(ncol(CE)))
CE[selected_columns] <- lapply(CE[selected_columns], 
                                  function(x) 
                                    replace(x,is.na(x), min(x, na.rm = T)
                                            ))
# Median Normalization
# CE <- as.matrix(CE)
# CE <- medianNormalization(CE, noLogTransform = TRUE)
# Reintroducing factored classes
CE <- cbind(CE, group)
CE <- as_tibble(CE)
# Cleaning colnames
CE <- clean_names(CE)
